Test 1 average: 75.83 with Std Deviation: 12.39
Test 2 average: 83.08 with Std Deviation: 19.44
Test 3 average: 76.58 with Std Deviation: 21.76
Test 4 average: 60.00 with Std Deviation: 43.59
```


